<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3672685>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2A–M. Dorsal habitus of Chalcolampra spp.; A, Chalcolampra sp.; B, Chalcolampra sp., length 4.8 mm; C, Chalcolampra speculifera Sharp, length 8.7 mm; D, Chalcolampra sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3672685/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3672687>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3A–F. Habits and structures of Chalcolampra spp.; A, Chalcolampra sp., dorsal habitus; B, Chalcolampra crassa (Broun), dorsal habitus of holotype; C, Chalcolampra sp., lateral view, length; D, Chalcolampra speculifera Sharp, detail of head; E Chalcolampra sp., detail of head; F, Chalcolampra sp., ventral view of anterior portion of body." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3672687/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3672719>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18A–E. Subantennal grooves (ventral view of heads, A–C) and prothoracic glandular ducts. A, Maurodus cinctiger; B, Maurodus lepidus; C, Maurodus maculatus; D, Chalcolampra sp., dorsal view through cleared prothorax; E, same, detail." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3672719/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

